Maddock Films presents "Thamma"
In Cinemas on 21st October.

#NoraFatehi #Dilbar #Thamma

Cast: Ayushmann Khurrana, Rashmika Mandanna, Paresh Rawal, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Faisal Malik, Rachit Singh

Haan, Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Aankhon Ko Aankhon Se Kisi Ki Chaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Pyaar Saccha Agar Chahiye
Toh Dua Mein Asar Chahiye
Buzdilon Ka Nahi Kaam Yeh
Pyaar Mein Toh Jigar Chahiye

Ishq Hua Par Khulke Izhaar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Dilbar Ki Aankhon Ka Didar Na Kiya
Kya Khaak Woh Jiya Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya

Na Kiya
Na Kiya, Jisne Pyaar Na Kiya
Kya Kiya, Kya Kiya
Kya Kiya, Jisne Pyar Na Kiya

snippet.title: 1,00,000 UC M762 SPECTRE SHREDDER OPENING | JONATHAN IS BACK!! | BGMI!
snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

Redbull Athlete 🧢
BGIS 2025 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2025 Finals MVP 👑
BGIS 2025 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
BMPS 2024 2nd Runner up 🥉
BGMS 2022 MVP 🏆
BGMS 2022 Runner up 🥈
BGIS 2021 Overall Top Fragger 🎯
PMWL #2 Overall Fragger 💣
PMCO Globals #4 Fragger 💣
PMPL 2020 Finals #2 Fragger 🎯
PMPL 2020 Finals Runner up 🥈
PMIS 2020 Top Fragger 🎯
PMIS 2020 India Champions 🏆
PMCO 2019 Fall Split SA Champion 🏆


 Follow Me & Stay Connected!

💬 Discord - https://discord.gg/jonathan

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Survival Stage | Day 1

The final chance to reach the Grand Finals is here. The 16 remaining teams from the Semi Finals who fell short of the Top 8 now face off in an intense BGMI survival battle. Every match counts and every fight could end their journey. Only the Top 8 teams will move forward to the Grand Finals.

Expect clutch plays, unpredictable zone shifts, and all-out chaos as these teams fight to stay alive and push the game Beyond Limits!

snippet.title: Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music
snippet.description:
Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music 

#payalkikhanak 
#पायल_की_खनक
#payal_ki_khanak
#पायल_की_खनक_से_जगेंगे_सजना
#payal_ki_khanak_se_jagege_sajna
#anilrawatkegane 
#anilrawat 
#anil_rawat 
#anilrawatsong
#अनिल_रावत_सोंग
payal ki khanak anil rawat song
पायल की खनक अनिल रावत सोंग
anil rawat viral song
अनिल रावत वायरल सोंग
payal ki khanak viral song



हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.title: Tu Subah Hai - Diwali Full Animation | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When love is true, sacrifice follows. When courage rises, legends are born. This Diwali, let emotions ignite the battlefield.

Experience the emotion. Feel the battle. 

Lyrics: 

Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.
Tu dua hai,
ya sazaa hai,
ya koi taaron ki kehkashan hai.
​

Saari dildaari teri,
yeh ishqdaari teri,
sudh-budh khoyi maine,
chadhi hai khumaari teri.
Khud se hua alag,
tujhse mila jo mere,
yaara.... yaara...
tujhse mila toh khud ko haara.
​

Ishq mein tere duniya se kya,
shaitanon se bhi lad jaaun,
bas tujhko hi main paaun.
​
Ek prem hi hai sach,
baaki sab toh yahaan pe jhootha hai re,
mujhko tujh mein mil jaana re, mil jaana re.​

Jab tak meri saans chalti,
mera har ik taana-baana tera hai... tera hai...
Roshni hai jab tak teri mere dil mein,
toh zara bhi na andhera hai... andhera hai...

​Saans meri ruk jaaye toh bhi,
teri khushboo saath mein hogi.
Lau jali meri aankhon mein,
toh jeet apni preet ki hogi.

​
Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.

Music: Akshay & IP
Lyrics: IP Singh
Singers: IP Singh, Sudhir Yaduvanshi
Music Arranged & Produced: Hrishikesh Gangan, Akshay Raheja
Mix & Master: Ashwin Kulkarni

snippet.title: Predator: Badlands | Final Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the new trailer for Predator: Badlands. Experience the film only in theaters and IMAX November 7.

Set in the future on a deadly remote planet, “Badlands” follows a young Predator outcast (played by newcomer Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi) who finds an unlikely ally in Thia (Emmy and Golden Globe nominee Elle Fanning) as he embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary. Produced by John Davis, Dan Trachtenberg, Marc Toberoff, Ben Rosenblatt and Brent O’Connor, “Predator: Badlands” opens exclusively in movie theaters on November 7 in IMAX, Dolby Cinema, RealD (3D), Cinemark XD, 4DX, ScreenX and premium screens everywhere.

snippet.description:

This will include: 3 YouTube titles, Odia structured description, hashtags, and tags.
(For the next adhyayas, we can just replace “Adhyaya-1” with the respective number and change only the intro line if needed.)

🌸 ନମିତା ଅଗ୍ରୱାଲ୍ ଙ୍କ ସୁନ୍ଦର ସ୍ୱରରେ କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାହାତ୍ମ୍ୟ 📖
ଆଜିର ପ୍ରସଙ୍ଗ – ଅଧ୍ୟାୟ 1
କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାସର ପବିତ୍ରତା, ଉପବାସ ଓ ପୁଣ୍ୟର କଥାକୁ ଶୁଣନ୍ତୁ ଓ ନିଜ ଜୀବନକୁ ପବିତ୍ର କରନ୍ତୁ।

📖 ଆଜିର ବିଷୟ
କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାସର ଗୁରୁତ୍ୱ

ପ୍ରଥମ ଅଧ୍ୟାୟର କାହାଣୀ

🎤 ଉପସ୍ଥାପନା – Namita Agrawal
📺 ପ୍ରସାରଣ – Sidharth Utsav

#KartikaMahatmya #NamitaAgrawal #Sidharth Bhakti #SidharthUtsav #KartikaBrata #OdiaSpiritual #KartikaMasa #BhaktiPravachan #OdiaDevotional #SidharthTV

ବରଷକ ବାର ମାସ ମଧ୍ୟରେ କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାସ ସବୁଠୁ ପବିତ୍ର ମାସ l ଏହି ମାସର ମାହାତ୍ମ୍ୟ ମହାନ l ଏହି ମାସର ପ୍ରତ୍ୟେକ ଦିନ ସନ୍ଧ୍ୟା ବେଳେ ତୁଳସୀ ଚଉରା ମୂଳେ ଆକାଶ ଦୀପ ଜାଳି ପିତୃ ପୁରୁଷଙ୍କୁ ସ୍ମରଣ କରାଯାଏ l ସେମାନଙ୍କ ପଥକୁ ଆଲୋକିତ କରାଯାଏ l 
କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ, ଧର୍ମ ଅର୍ଜନ କରିବାର ମାସ l
କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ, ପୁଣ୍ୟ ଅର୍ଜନ କରିବାର ମାସ l
କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାସରେ ପ୍ରତ୍ୟେକ ଦିନ କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାହାତ୍ମ୍ୟ ପଢିଲେ ଓ ଶୁଣିଲେ ସବୁ ପାପ କ୍ଷୟ ହୋଇଥାଏ  l ମାସସାରା ହବିଷ୍ୟାଳି ମାନେ ସନ୍ଧ୍ୟାରେ ଏକତ୍ରିତ ହୋଇ କାର୍ତ୍ତିକ ମାହାତ୍ମ୍ୟର ଗୋଟିଏ ଗୋଟିଏ ଅଧ୍ୟାୟ ଶ୍ରବଣ କରି ନିଜକୁ ପ୍ରଭୁଙ୍କ ନିକଟରେ ସମର୍ପଣ କରିଥାନ୍ତି l

snippet.title: Thangapoovey - Full Video | Madharaasi | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil presents the full video of “Thangapoovey” from the much-awaited film Madharaasi, written and directed by acclaimed filmmaker A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth in lead roles, this soulful track is composed by none other than Anirudh Ravichander, known for his chart-topping melodies and heart-touching compositions. Thangapoovey blends emotion with melody, capturing the essence of love and longing with poetic visuals and heartfelt lyrics.

With its mesmerizing tune and lyrical depth, Thangapoovey promises to strike a chord with music lovers and fans of Tamil cinema alike. Whether you're a follower of romantic Tamil songs or a die-hard fan of Anirudh’s music, this lyrical video is a must-watch. As anticipation builds for Madharaasi, this song sets the perfect tone, offering a glimpse into the film’s emotional landscape.

रचा है सृष्टि को जिस प्रभु ने
हर सांस मे हो सुमिरन तेरा
श्री मन नारायण नारायण हरि हरि
नारायण की अजब हैं माया
श्री विष्णु अमृतवाणी
हरि नाम की माला जपले
ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय
विष्णु जी के 108 नाम
भगवान मेरी नैया उस पार

hi.title: वीरवार स्पेशल  | Vishnu Ji Ke Bhajan | विष्णु जी के भजन |Ekadashi Bhajan | Hari Ke Bhajan | Bhajan
hi.description:
वीरवार स्पेशल  | Vishnu Ji Ke Bhajan | विष्णु जी के भजन |Ekadashi Bhajan | Hari Ke Bhajan | Bhajan

तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

⭐Bhajan : 
रचा है सृष्टि को जिस प्रभु ने
हर सांस मे हो सुमिरन तेरा
श्री मन नारायण नारायण हरि हरि
नारायण की अजब हैं माया
श्री विष्णु अमृतवाणी
हरि नाम की माला जपले
ॐ नमो भगवते वासुदेवाय
विष्णु जी के 108 नाम
भगवान मेरी नैया उस पार
ॐ जय जगदीश हरे

⭐Singer : Upasana Mehta & Sanchit 
⭐Lyrics :  Archana Agarwa & Sachin Tulsiyan &Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)

snippet.title: Franklin Buys Gaming PC for Kids! 😍 Shinchan Great Escape from Police 🚔 | GTA 5 Malayalam
snippet.description:
Franklin and Shinchan are chilling at home with Franklin’s family when Trevor and his son visit. Trevor’s son shows off his brand-new gaming laptop and refuses to let the kids touch it! 😡 Franklin feels bad for his kids and decides to get them the best gaming PC ever! 💻🔥

He and Shinchan go to Simeon’s shop, but since it’s Sunday, all shops are closed 😭 Simeon gives them a secret idea — a truck full of gaming PCs is in a police-guarded godown! 🚓 Franklin and Shinchan go on a crazy mission to steal it and escape from the police in true GTA style! 😎

👉 Watch till the end for a funny twist and the kids’ reaction! ❤️
💬 Comment your favorite part!
📺 Subscribe for more GTA 5 Malayalam stories featuring Franklin, Shinchan, and friends!

snippet.title: Meri Zindagi Ke Malik  |  Imaan Beiman  |  Alka Yagnik  |  Udit Narayan Songs  |  Neelam
snippet.description:
Welcome to our special throwback on the journey to the golden era of the 90s featuring Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan's rare gem – Meri Zindagi Ke Malik from the movie Imaan Beiman. Their voices not only defined but exemplified the true meaning of romance in their songs, leaving listeners spellbound and hearts filled with love. Meri Zindagi Ke Malik is a manifestation of the romantic aura of the90ss, captivating listeners in the beautiful melody. 

Meri Zindagi Ke Malik

Let's embark on a beautiful journey with these romantic songs that evoke a thousand emotions, leaving us reminiscing about forgotten love. We invite you to engage with us, leave your comments, and let us know which is your favorite romantic song from the list. Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe if you enjoyed the journey as much as we did curating it for you. 

Let the magic of music from Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan continue to live on...

#AlkaYagnik #UditNarayan #MeriZindagiKeMalik #90sHindiSongs #RomanticSongs

localized.title: Meri Zindagi Ke Malik  |  Imaan Beiman  |  Alka Yagnik  |  Udit Narayan Songs  |  Neelam
localized.description:
Welcome to our special throwback on the journey to the golden era of the 90s featuring Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan's rare gem – Meri Zindagi Ke Malik from the movie Imaan Beiman. Their voices not only defined but exemplified the true meaning of romance in their songs, leaving listeners spellbound and hearts filled with love. Meri Zindagi Ke Malik is a manifestation of the romantic aura of the90ss, captivating listeners in the beautiful melody. 

Meri Zindagi Ke Malik

Let's embark on a beautiful journey with these romantic songs that evoke a thousand emotions, leaving us reminiscing about forgotten love. We invite you to engage with us, leave your comments, and let us know which is your favorite romantic song from the list. Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe if you enjoyed the journey as much as we did curating it for you. 

Let the magic of music from Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan continue to live on...

#AlkaYagnik #UditNarayan #MeriZindagiKeMalik #90sHindiSongs #RomanticSongs 

Credits :

Song: Meri Zindagi Ke Malik
Album: Imaan Beiman
Artist: Alka Yagnik | Udit Narayan
Music Director: Rajesh Roshan
Lyricist: Indiwar

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: #Video | Raat Mein Bata De | रात में बता दे | #AnkushRaja & #KhushbuTiwari KT | Ft. #DivyaRalhan
snippet.description:
“Raat Mein Bata De | रात में बता दे” – एक मजेदार और रोमांटिक भोजपुरिया गाना, जिसमें अंकुश राजा और खुश्बू तिवारी (KT) की जोड़ी ने अपनी आवाज़ से धूम मचा दी है। वहीं अंकुश राजा और दिव्या राल्हन की शानदार ऑन-स्क्रीन केमिस्ट्री और रंगीन विजुअल्स इस गाने को और भी खास बना देते हैं।
धमाकेदार बीट्स, दिलचस्प बोल और जोश से भरी परफॉर्मेंस से सजा ये गाना आपके दिलों को ज़रूर छू लेगा। इसे मिस मत करिए – शेयर करिए और झूम उठिए!

🎶 Song Credits:
► Song Name: Raat Mein Bata De | रात में बता दे
► Singer: Ankush Raja & Khushbu Tiwari (KT)
► Lyrics: Chhotu Yadav
► Music: Vicky Vox
► Ft: Ankush Raja & Divya Ralhan
► Director & Choreographer: Lakkie Vishwakarma
► DOP: Yogesh Singh
► Edit: Rohan Raut (Ninja)
► DI: Rohit Singh
► Production: Akash Vishwakarma
► Music Label: Leechee Music
► Company: Leechee Entertainment Private Limited

🔔 Subscribe करने के लिए क्लिक करें – https://www.youtube.com/@LeecheeMusicBhojpuri

Follow us on:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/share/1GCSg6qXqZ/
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/leecheemusic_bhojpuri

Reach out to us on: office@leecheemusic.com

#ankushraja #khushbutiwari #divyaralhan #newbhojpurisong2025 

Lyrics:
पहली पहली रात मैं तो सोई भी नहीं
खुश थी इतनी ज्यादा कि मैं रोई भी नहीं
पहली पहली रात मैं तो सो ई भी नहीं
खुश थी इतनी ज्या दा कि मैं रोई भी नहीं

उसने बोला शरम का पर्दा हटा दे
क्या करती हो सैया के संग रात में बता दे

जीती या हरी तू लव वाला खेल में
सब कुछ बताओ मुझे डार्लिंग डिटेल में
कह दे अपने मजनू से फीलिंग तू दिल के
कैसा लगा तुझको पियवा से मिलके
सेज पे पियवा का किया

हाथ धरा फिर चुम्मा लिया
उसने आगे क्या किया
अरे अपनी तरफ घुमा लिया
 और क्या हुआ

अरे बो लो अरे बो लो बो लो सोचो मत

अरे इसके आगे पुछो मत
उसे बोला जरा सा कुंडी लगा दे
क्या करती हो साइयां के संग रात में बता दे

आया वो नियारा हंस के
पकड़ा कमरिया को कस के

हटा दे हटा दे हटा दे शर्म हया सब हटा दे
बता दे बता दे बता दे और डिटेल में बता दे

छोटू अंकुश राजा अब तू मुझको भुला दे
क्या करती हो सैंया के संग रात में बता दे

snippet.description:
Today I Upgraded my very own brainrot. Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens.

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/11775558/Foltyns-Family#!/about

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/realfoltyn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

Laxmi Aarti in Hindi,lakshmi aarti,maha lakshmi aarti,लक्ष्मी आरती हिंदी,लक्ष्मी आरती हिंदी में,Om Jai Laxmi Mata,om jai lakshmi mata,jai lakshmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata,जय लक्ष्मी माता,ॐ जय लक्ष्मी माता,mahalaxmi songs,om jai laxmi mata,laxmi aarti,laxmi ji ki aarti,lakshmi mata ki aarti,lakshmi ji ki aarti,aarti lakshmi ji ki,aarti laxmi ji ki,laxmi mata ki aarti,laxmi mata aarti,jai laxmi mata aarti,maa laxmi aarti,aarti lakshmi mata ki

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. A person who recites this Aarti with true devotion is blessed with wealth and prosperity and a good family life. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

snippet.title: Kuanra Punei & Gajalaxmi Brata Katha | ଗଜଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ବ୍ରତ ଗାଥା ଓ ପୂଜା ବିଧି | Namita Agrawal
snippet.description:
🌸 Listen to the sacred *Gajalaxmi Brata Katha* (ମା' ଗଜଲକ୍ଷ୍ମୀ ବ୍ରତ କଥା) narrated with devotion by Namita Agrawal, along with the divine folk song *“Kuanra Punei Janha Go Phula Baulabeni”*. This special video brings you the powerful story (କାହାଣୀ) and puja vidhi (ପୂଜା ବିଧି) of Ma Gajalaxmi, observed during Kuanra Punei and Kartika Purnima in Odisha.

📖 Watch this video to understand the spiritual importance of the brata, the rituals to be performed, and the blessings of Goddess Laxmi.

🛕 Content Includes:
- Gajalaxmi Brata Katha (Odia narration)
- Puja Vidhi & Niyama
- Traditional Kuanra Punei song by Namita Agrawal

🎤 Voice & Song: Namita Agrawal  
🎼 Music Label: Sidharth Music  
🎊 Occasion: Kuanra Punei /  Gajalaxmi Puja  
📺 Language: Odia (ଓଡ଼ିଆ)
